<li class='cover' id='bookCover_39988'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/39988.Matilda"><img alt="Matilda" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388793265l/39988._SX98_.jpg" />
